---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - StaubRacing">
  <article class="about-page">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>Hey, I'm Chris.</p>

    <p>
      I spent my early twenties on the ramp at MSP, keeping tired 727s flying through Minnesota winters on midnight shifts. That's where I learned that everything is fixable if you're stubborn enough and willing to work in the cold.
    </p>

    <p>
      Now I'm a manufacturing engineer in the medical device world â€” FDA regulations, validation protocols, and the kind of precision that doesn't leave room for "close enough." By night, I write code. React Native apps, AWS infrastructure, homelab experiments, websites (you're looking at one), and whatever else I can't stop tinkering with.
    </p>

    <p>
      On weekends, I race motorcycles. Central Road Racing here in Minnesota, number 106, Ultralight and Middleweight classes, five years in. A 2014 KX450F for supermoto and a 2009 ZX6R that I've rebuilt more times than I'll admit.
    </p>

    <p>
      Same approach to all of it, take it apart, figure out how it works, make it better.
    </p>

    <p>Thanks for stopping by.</p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 65ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  p:first-of-type {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-page {
      padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    p:first-of-type {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
